reviewText: instead of buying this DVD which does not contain the entire SuperFetch series, you can watch the complete series on Amazon Instant Video! It is a very good series and gets great reviews ;)

The show is awesome, but this DVD is only for six episodes of it! I had expected, given the price I was paying, to receive the entire first season. Needs to be much more clearly marked that this DVD does NOT contain the full season of this show.
